    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >INFO</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此游戏需要<strong>两名玩家</strong>和<strong>耳机</strong>以进行流畅的沟通。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119740/extras/c71a7ff26198653f33d3aabe39fc01a2.avif?t=1734969484\" width=612 height=120 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的团队由两个最顶尖的小偷组成，无需任何问题。这一直都是这样，直到一个神秘客户雇佣你去偷取一个未知物品。目标？机密。报酬？高得让人无法拒绝。决定谁负责情报，谁潜入设施，在这个非对称合作解谜游戏中完成任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119740/extras/a076d2a83c1423e707ee640fa6f3e012.poster.avif?t=1734969484\" width=612 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119740/extras/a076d2a83c1423e707ee640fa6f3e012.webm?t=1734969484\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独特功能</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>非对称合作。</strong> 在不同地点工作，使用工具和解决谜题来帮助对方。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>引人入胜的故事。</strong> 体验充满转折、多种结局和重要选择的剧情。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>创新谜题。</strong> 每个谜题都带来全新玩法，需要团队合作才能解决。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏内语音聊天。</strong> 使用老式对讲机，与伙伴保持联系。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>独特的关卡设计。</strong> 探索令人惊叹且充满挑战的环境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受游戏吧。~ No More Sleep</p>",
